packets.name: CV-BOT dark left leg

packets.description:
The CV-BOT comes as a 5 piece suit 2 arms 2x legs 1x body and head rarity 1/1in dark.
CV-BOT is programmed to patrol and protect Cryptovoxels and locate the finest builds. 
Created by the "First Avatars" Known as the "Nolanites" after the "Great Unprogramming" 
this Bot is the memory of CV, all knowing all remembering.
